This prompt was found here:
  https://codereview.stackexchange.com/questions/37521/marbles-game-with-classes

The number of marbles in the initial pile will be random amount between 10 and 100.
Each player must choose between 1 and half of the remaining pile of marbles to remove.
The player stuck with the last marble loses the game.
The computer will randomly be placed into simple or smart mode.
The player who goes first will also be chosen at random.

This problem is good for AI testing/creation and to create a framework similar to the AI roomba project.

